{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"94adc3cf-aca8-45ef-8462-03fe42ae4edd","content":"I can help guide you through analyzing your .NET crash dump. The `dump-collect` skill I have is only for **collecting** dumps, not analyzing them — so let me help directly.\n\n**Common tools for .dmp analysis:**\n\n| Tool | Platform |\n|---|---|\n| `dotnet-dump analyze` | Cross-platform |\n| `lldb` + SOS plugin | Linux / macOS |\n| WinDbg + SOS | Windows |\n\n**Quick start with `dotnet-dump`:**\n\n```bash\n# Install if needed\ndotnet tool install -g dotnet-dump\n\n# Open the dump\ndotnet-dump analyze your-file.dmp\n```\n\n**Useful commands once inside the analyzer:**\n\n| Command | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `clrstack` | Managed call stack of current thread |\n| `clrthreads` | List all managed threads |\n| `pe` | Print last exception |\n| `dumpheap -stat` | Heap summary (for OOM crashes) |\n| `setthread <id>` then `clrstack` | Inspect other threads |\n\nWould you like me to walk you through running any of these, or do you have the `.dmp` file in this environment so I can analyze it directly?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"a37651d0-5672-4d58-be58-b3a08cc7b318","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a .dmp crash dump file from a .NET application and wants to analyze it to find the root cause of a crash. Let me help them with this.\n\nLooking at the available skills, I see there's a `dump-collect` skill, but its description says it's for **collecting** crash dumps, NOT for **analyzing** them. It explicitly says \"DO NOT USE FOR: analyzing or debugging dumps, post-mortem investigation with lldb/windbg/dotnet-dump analyze.\"\n\nSo the `dump-collect` skill is not appropriate here. Let me provide guidance directly.\n\nFor analyzing .NET crash dumps, the typical tools are:\n\n\n- `dotnet-dump analyze` (cross-platform)\n- `lldb` with SOS plugin (Linux)\n- WinDbg with SOS (Windows)\n\nI should ask where the dump file is located and what platform they're working on so I can give them the most relevant guidance.","outputTokens":517,"requestId":"AC08:32CD37:13CE178:1648E7A:6A067273"},"id":"cf23a605-7701-407f-8b03-cbbd08a44584","timestamp":"2026-05-15T01:10:24.218Z","parentId":"3d55dc2b-5e53-4db3-a314-7f481e4e4cdb"}
